                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Providence</placeName> the <date>13<hi rend=\"sup\"\n                        >th</hi> of Jany 1854</date></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <addressee>Leeser Esq</addressee>\n                <add>?</add>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Sir I beg leave to inform you<lb/> that we have established a\n                congregation here in<lb/>\n                <placeName>Providence</placeName>. The whole members met together last<lb/>\n                <date>Sunday</date>, and signed their names for supporting<lb/> the society with 50\n                cnt each every week, and named<lb/> it (<add>בני ישראל</add>) Bene Israel. They\n                elected their officers,<lb/> namely <persName>Mr Pareira</persName> President,\n                    <persName>Mr. Frank</persName>, <persName>Mr Stern</persName>,<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr Solomon</persName>, and <persName>Mr Steinberg</persName>\n                <sic>Comittee</sic>, <persName>Mr.<lb/> Hirschhorn</persName> has been elected as\n                Sec. and treasurer.<lb/> They engaged me as their Minister, and promised<lb/> me\n                $5.50 cnt weekly <sic>sallary</sic> without other income.<lb/> They also promised me\n                to have a hall ready<lb/> to perform and to deliver our Prayers to<lb/> our holy\n                God, <sic>befor</sic> (<add>ר\"ח אלול</add>) and to fix every<lb/> thing in a\n                suitable manner. They bought already<lb/> a (<add>בית הקברות</add>), and are in\n                undertaking of making around<lb/> a fence, that is all I have to inform you<lb/>\n                about it at present. I hope I shall be<lb/> able to inform you more about it next<lb/>\n                <del>week</del> month. You will please send me the<lb/> Occident as soon as\n                possible.</p>\n            <p>I allow me to <del>signed</del> sign</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">your friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(6)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Joseph Spiro</persName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3wh2f157/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
